\c 34
\s Kufa nekuvigwa kwaMozisi
\p
\v 1 Zvino Mozisi wakakwira kubva pamapani ekwaMoabhu achienda kugomo reNebho, nhongonya yePisiga iri pakatarisana neJeriko\x + Num. 27.12.\x*. Jehovha ndokumutaridza nyika yose, Giriyadhi kusvika kuDhani\x + Vato. 18.29.\x*,
\v 2 neNafutari yose, nenyika yaEfuremu, naManase, nenyika yose yaJudha, kusvika pagungwa rekupedzisira\x + 11.24.\x*;
\v 3 nechamhembe, nebani remupata weJeriko\x + Gen.. 13.12. 19.17. 2 Sam. 18.23.\x*, guta remichindwe\x + Vato. 1.16. 3.13. 2 Makor. 28.15.\x*, kusvika Zoari\x + Gen.. 14.2,8. 19.22.\x*.
\v 4 Zvino Jehovha akati kwaari: Iyi inyika yandakapikira Abhurahama, Isaka, naJakove, ndichiti: Ndichaipa kumbeu yako\x + Gen.. 12.7. 50.24.\x*; ndakakuita kuti uone nemeso ako, asi haungayambukiriko\x + 3.27. 32.52.\x*.
\p
\v 5 Zvino Mozisi muranda waJehovha wakafirapo munyika yaMoabhu, zvichienderana neshoko raJehovha.
\v 6 Zvino wakamuviga pamupata panyika yaMoabhu, pakatarisana neBheti-Peori\x + Num. 23.28.\x*; asi hakuna munhu anoziva guva rake kusvika nhasi\x + Jud. 9.\x*.
\p
\v 7 Zvino Mozisi waiva wemakore zana nemakumi maviri pakufa kwake\x + 31.2.\x*; meso ake aiva asati osvibirirwa, neutsva hwake husati hwatiza\x + Gen.. 27.1. 1 Sam. 3.2. Gen.. 48.10. Josh. 14.10,11. 1 Sam. 4.15.\x*.
\p
\v 8 Vana vaIsraeri vakachema Mozisi pamapani ekwaMoabhu mazuva makumi matatu; saizvozvo mazuva emariro ekuchema Mozisi akapera\x + Num. 20.29. Gen.. 50.3.\x*.
\p
\v 9 Zvino Joshua mwanakomana waNuni waiva azere nemweya wekuchenjera\x + Isa. 11.2.\x*; nokuti Mozisi waiva aisa maoko ake pamusoro pake; vana vaIsraeri ndokumuteerera, ndokuita Jehovha sezvaakaraira Mozisi\x + Num. 27.18,23.\x*.
\p
\v 10 Zvino hakuna kumukazve muporofita pakati paIsraeri wakaita saMozisi\x + 18.15,18.\x*, Jehovha waakaziva chiso nechiso\x + Eki. 33.11. Vato. 6.22. Num. 12.8. Det. 5.4.\x*;
\v 11 pazviratidzo zvose nezvishamiso, Jehovha zvaakamutuma kunoita panyika yeEgipita, kuna Farao nekuvaranda vake vose nekunyika yake\x + 4.34. 7.19.\x* yose;
\v 12 neparuoko rwose urwo rwune simba\x + 4.34.\x*, nepakutyisa kukuru kwese\x + 4.34.\x*, Mozisi kwaakaita pamberi pemeso aIsraeri wose.